          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
          <div class=".col-xs-12 .col-sm-2 .col-lg-8">
            <%= image_tag("sample-menu.jpg", :class => "menu-image img-responsive") %>
          </div>
          <div class=".col-xs-6 .col-lg-4">
            <h1 class="work-text">Another Title goes here</h1>
            <p class="work-paragraph-right">Donec orci odio, pulvinar ac pellentesque nec, ultricies eu dolor. Aliquam varius auctor facilisis. Mauris elementum dolor ac elit fermentum scelerisque. Maecenas sed molestie enim. Duis eget cursus ex. Duis semper, dui vel tempus facilisis.</p>
          </div>
